item.title: cesR Data Analysis on gender and durarion
item.description: Introduction The data is about Canadian Election Study and I choose the Web survey in this study to explore some interesting findings. Data Data description There are 620 variables and 37822 observations in this data set and there are some interesting variable that caught my eyes. Some initial explorations The variables we focus on are: the gender of participants in the Web survey the citizenship of participants in the Web survey
